{
  "title": "Hướng dẫn chơi trò chơi",
  "html": "<main><header class=\"section-page-header\"><div class=\"row d-flex justify-content-between\"><div class=\"col col-sm-10\"></div><!----></div><!----><h1>Hướng dẫn chơi trò chơi</h1><p class=\"text-secondary mb-0\">Hướng dẫn tạo lại các thành phần trò chơi phổ biến.</p><!----></header><!----><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-9 print-w-100\"><div class=\"b-img\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Gameplay Tutorials\" width=\"1920\" height=\"335\" loading=\"lazy\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" decoding=\"auto\" ng-img=\"true\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/ae073b4c-d91c-4b1a-8210-4f7dbb99e155?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335\" srcset=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/ae073b4c-d91c-4b1a-8210-4f7dbb99e155?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335 1x, https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/ae073b4c-d91c-4b1a-8210-4f7dbb99e155?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=3840&amp;height=670 2x\"></div><!----><!----><!----><header class=\"document-header mb-3 d-lg-none d-print-none\"><content-nav class=\"content-nav is-collapsible\" ngh=\"6\"><!----><!----></content-nav></header><!----><article><!----><!----><div document-content-blocks-renderer=\"\" class=\"d-block\" ngh=\"10\"><div id=\"content-blocks-renderer\" class=\"content-blocks-renderer\"><block-switch-control class=\"block-switch-control\" ngh=\"7\"><!----></block-switch-control><block-switch-info class=\"block-switch-info\" ngh=\"8\"><!----></block-switch-info><blocks-renderer id=\"blocks-renderer\" ngh=\"9\"><!----><block-markdown ngh=\"2\"><div class=\"block-markdown\"><p>Phần này chứa các hướng dẫn về cách sử dụng hệ thống của Unreal Engine để tạo lại các tính năng phổ biến trong lối chơi.</p>\n\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"A tutorial for adding Components to Actors.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:adding-components-to-an-actor-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Adding Components to an Actor\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/24df3ead-e463-41bb-b28b-a109e4eb4281/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"In this Tutorial, you will create a playable character that exhibits different forms of Character Movement.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:setting-up-character-movement\" page-name=\"Setting Up Character Movement\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/65e47442-9fa1-4a73-9b2b-7a8816db0e1f/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"A tutorial on how to find Actors in your scene by using Blueprint Scripting / C++.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:finding-actors-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Finding Actors\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/c6e8052d-8185-4bed-adbf-b2245f5525ab/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"A tutorial for respawning player characters in Unreal Engine.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:respawning-a-player-character\" page-name=\"Respawning a Player Character\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/bae7c703-2e4b-48de-a8fd-b5ece972a280/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Overview of how to save and load your game\" href=\"#unreal-doc:saving-and-loading-your-game-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Saving and Loading Your Game\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/1288ee4c-d1b7-4b90-a405-7f70035d025e/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"A tutorial for possessing different pawns in Unreal Engine.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:possessing-pawns-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Possessing Pawns\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/e7eec1e8-8e33-4ea4-871b-5c2b6f0c6176/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"A tutorial for setting up a Game Mode in Unreal Engine.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:setting-up-a-game-mode-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Setting Up a Game Mode\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/af73052b-e5c1-4246-a6e2-2e89b95f061d/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"A tutorial to for using the OnHit Event in Unreal.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:using-the-onhit-event\" page-name=\"Using the OnHit Event\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/a4d2d56e-8152-4654-bd19-233cf9337e2a/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n</div></block-markdown><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></blocks-renderer></div><!----></div></article><tags-list class=\"mt-1 d-print-none\" ngh=\"11\"><!----><ul class=\"labels-list is-links\"><li class=\"labels-item\"><!----><a class=\"labels-link\" href=\"/community/search?query=gameplay\">lối chơi</a><!----></li><li class=\"labels-item\"><!----><a class=\"labels-link\" href=\"/community/search?query=blueprints\">bản thiết kế</a><!----></li><li class=\"labels-item\"><!----><a class=\"labels-link\" href=\"/community/search?query=programming\">lập trình</a><!----></li><!----></ul><!----></tags-list><!----><div class=\"col-lg-3 d-none d-lg-block d-print-none\"><!----></div></div><!----><!----><!----></main>",
